        "subject": "LU-18655 tests: fix sanity-quota wait_delete_completed",
        "message": "LU-18655 tests: fix sanity-quota wait_delete_completed\n\n1. Print error in sanity-quota if wait_delete_completed()\n   called from cleanup_quota_test failed. As appropriate\n   test case would be marked as failed, it makes sense to\n   capture debug logs.\n2. Fix sanity-quota_6 to create files only on ost1.\n\nLustre-change: https://review.whamcloud.com/57500\nLustre-commit: af936b6deac70fca37e3ae4f139f48362029cc3e\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Sergey Cheremencev <scherementsev@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: Ifff7c1a221c0d1fd8b4a494b67e02cc03b74eb68\nReviewed-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/61262\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Artem Blagodarenko <ablagodarenko@ddn.com>\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\n"
